76561198002986817,Recommended,219780,31674983,Posted: 10 May,all,Phantom Virus,"If you enjoy fantasy RPGs, like me, then this game is for you! It has everything you need. First, you get two games in one which is a great bonus. There is a great mount of content and plenty of secrets too. The story is actually decent, which is saying something. The game is fun, challanging at times, and gives you plenty of options. The game does freeze from time to time between loading screens but if you save often it isn't that big of a deal. The only negative is the ending is rather lackluster. Still, a fantastic game for anyone who enjoys this style of game. You need to add this game to your list if you truly love fantast rpgs."
